Procedure to delte lets encrypt Certificate
https://medium.com/@matthagemann/correct-way-to-delete-a-certbot-ssl-certificate-e8ee123e6e01

Command to delete lets encrypt certificate
sudo certbot delete

Command to renew lets encrypt certificate
certbot renew

